{"tid":1541591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有黃絲婆婆想提醒我地！！","createTime":"2019-09-04T15:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T17:53:39.000Z","uid":317379,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"12ecbcf4ca0a77776b17dc6a7d371924f16154d7","tid":1541591,"uid":317379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"［代友po 朋友係中學生］<br />\n<br />\n有日放學有個6x歲婆婆提醒我地以下兩點，佢話自己唔識用連登，希望我地可以幫手擺上嚟。<br />\n<br />\n1.發夢唔好再著全黑<br />\n要捉要打都第一個搵你，要帶多套衫，可以就著埋係入面，一除就得。<br />\n<br />\n2.俾人打要喊得有幾慘得幾慘，同用英文講救命<br />\n佢強調左好多次要大喊，吸引更多街坊過嚟之餘，最重要係引起外國關注，話俾外國知香港人好慘，引起國際輿論。<br />\n<br />\n最後，佢話佢咁老做唔到啲咩，最多間唔中出嚟行下，同埋繼續咁樣周圍同啲後生講，叫我地一定要小心！！唔想再見到我地受傷:("},{"pid":"2a49f8dcb0673d49e9a6886b3465c11cf34b93e6","tid":1541591,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NdLHvPz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdLHvPz.jpg&h=fca19d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcJFfrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcJFfrO.jpg&h=7f9dd8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjeJddu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeJddu.jpg&h=e690fd03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月6日 反濫捕 抗威權集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535223</a>"},{"pid":"8bf5f7ab52e2cc6de87078eb12a12a10c08ee04f","tid":1541591,"uid":283713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:19:32.000Z","msg":"岩啊，要大聲慘叫"},{"pid":"8055188568d23f577b47fe772a52813d111d1623"